  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "4 \u0b86\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd : \u0bae\u0bc0\u0bb3 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a \u0bae\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Risk of 4th Covid wave: Wear face masks again - State Medical Officers Association request",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Reinforce the wearing of face coverings in public places and re-implement the recommendations of the Covid Technical Committee.",
        "The Government Medical Officers Association has also requested the Director General of Health Services to sensitize the public about the possibility of another covid outbreak in the country.",
        "Dr. Haritha Aluthge, Secretary of the Medical Officers' Association commented in this regard,",
        "Omicron has a wide spread globally. Currently the enrollment rate has increased in various countries of the world including India and China.",
        "So spread information among general public to resume covid control measures immediately.",
        "We also request to reconvene the technical committee to implement the technical recommendations for re-wearing face masks to control the situation",
        "Mandatory wearing of masks in hospitals, public transport, places of public gatherings and other infectious persons",
        "Those who have not received the covid vaccine should get it properly. If the country goes into another covid pandemic by September we will not have enough vaccines to control the situation.",
        "The dollar crisis in the country will make it impossible to control another wave of Covid.",
        "We therefore appeal to the public to continue wearing face masks and get the fourth covid vaccine as soon as possible to control the spread of new covid strains.",
        "In this case, less than five infected people were identified in the previous period and now the number of confirmed Covid infection has increased to 80 within a month.",
        "A Covid death reported once a day, three or four days a week has been reported as one death a day and seven deaths a week.",
        "Therefore, media houses, responsible government and private organizations should take responsibility for warning the public about the spread of the new sub-variant of Covid and informing the people about the technical aspects to prevent the virus, he said."
      ],
